# Exclusion rules — fields that should NOT be obfuscated
#
# Format:
#   collection_regex::field_regex   skip field in matching collections only
#   field_regex                     skip field globally (all collections)
#
# Lines starting with # and empty lines are ignored.
# Regex is case-insensitive and must be a fullmatch on the field name.
#
# Examples:
#   .*-environments.*::name         preserve 'name' in *-environments* collections
#   .*-channels.*::name             preserve 'name' in *-channels* collections
#   slug                            preserve 'slug' everywhere
#   .*::_type                       preserve '_type' in every collection
